   <note>A letter from Nancy Reagan written on The White House stationery expressing her deep concern for the drug epidemic among young people and gratitude for those attending Kingsport`s Community Drug Awareness Week. Also included is a Proclamation signed by the Mayor of Kingsport, C. N. Spencer, declaring October 3-10, 1982, as Community Drug Awareness Week.</note>
